Notes: Stout earns sole possession of first place in the WIAC with the victory...
Stout opened second half on a 15-6 run over the first 6:28 and did not lead
by less than 13 points the rest of the way...Stout's 13th consecutive win over
SP at Johnson Fieldhouse...SP entered game ranked seventh nationally.
Game.Officials: Scott Doberstein,  Jeff Linehan,  Cheryl Kahler
